title: Ocean Front House Sept 15 to May 31/June 14
posting_body: ['Oceanfront Beach House for Rent near the drawbridge.', 'Private beach.', 'Clean and comfortable four bedroom home.', 'There are three floors, each has a bathroom.', 'The house is fully furnished and includes a large screen TV, dishwasher, washer, dryer and central air.', 'Fenced in backyard for privacy, three small decks, charcoal grill, beach chairs, toys, umbrellas and stairs to beach.', 'Located on the Hampton Harbor inlet and ocean so drawbridge is nearby, fishing boat traffic, tidal pools for younger children at low tide, private beach and safer area in basin for swimming during high tide.', 'Nice shade on the deck in the afternoon and the Hampton fireworks are visible from the house in-season.', 'Great location just minutes from route 495 and near Hampton Harbor with stores nearby, restaurants within walking distance, entertaining area of the beach to stay and beautiful at sunrise, year-round.', 'We do not allow smokers and are looking for clean, quiet people who will take good care of the property.', 'Lease is from October 1, 2022 to June 1, 2023.', 'Monthly rent is $3600 Includes Utilities.', 'Might have last weeks of September and Early weeks of June available at weekly rates if needed.']
